'''铍化锂''' 是一系列假想的[[金属互化物|金属互化物]] ，由[[锂|锂]] 和[[铍|铍]] 组成。它们可能具有 LiBe、 LiBe<sub>2</sub>、Li<sub>2</sub>Be、 LiBe<sub>3</sub>、 Li<sub>3</sub>Be、Li<sub>2</sub>Be<sub>3</sub>、Li<sub>3</sub>Be<sub>2</sub>、LiBe<sub>4</sub> 和 Li<sub>4</sub>Be。<ref name = ashcroft>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1038/nature06442 | title = Emergent reduction of electronic state dimensionality in dense ordered Li-Be alloys | year = 2008 | last1 = Feng | first1 = Ji | last2 = Hennig | first2 = Richard G. | last3 = Ashcroft | first3 = N. W. | last4 = Hoffmann | first4 = Roald | journal = Nature | volume = 451 | issue = 7177 | pages = 445–8 | pmid = 18216850| doi-access = free }}</ref> [[计算化学|计算化学]]表示这些化合物中有一些可以在非常高的压力和低温下[[超导|超导]]。 <ref name=ashcroft/><ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1103/PhysRevB.78.172501 | title = Ab initio study of superconducting hexagonal Be2Li under pressure | year = 2008 | last1 = Errea | first1 = Ion | last2 = Martinez-Canales | first2 = Miguel | last3 = Bergara | first3 = Aitor | journal = Physical Review B | volume = 78 | issue = 17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/j.ssc.2011.09.032 | title = Superconductivity in ordered LiBe alloy under high pressure: A first-principles study | year = 2012 | last1 = Xu | first1 = Ying | last2 = Chen | first2 = Changbo | last3 = Wu | first3 = Baojia | journal = Solid State Communications | volume = 152 | issue = 2 | pages = 151}}</ref>

